result.execSummary:
The defendant Andrew Shane Stensrud was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Andrew Shane Stensrud is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Andrew Shane Stensrud was found guilty of Bail Jumping-Misdemeanor, a class A misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(a).
